highlights.text: Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Chennai. Jimikki Ponnu is the highest at #4.
Kadhale Kadhale by Shankar Mahadevan and Padmalatha is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chennai, up 61 spots at #39.
Idhazhin Oram - The Innocence of Love by Anirudh Ravichander and Ajesh has been on Top Songs Chennai the longest, at 67 weeks straight.
Naadodi Mannan by G. V. Prakash and Anthony Daasan is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chennai at #82.
